Instructions
------------
   A picks up pieces to move or attack (start)
   L selects territories (after pick up)
   A attacks or moves (after selecting a non-owned territory)
   X places pieces (after getting one piece and move done)
   B puts pieces down (after next selection?)
   P Only ready pieces (colored) can move or attack (after next selection?)
   P Pieces can move or attack every six seconds (after next selection?)
   P Owning more territories creates new pieces faster (after owning >= 4 territories)
